{"tid":1589602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10.1 200萬人係咪一定去港島， 200萬人唔可以塞到九龍尖咀？","createTime":"2019-09-23T10:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T12:26:35.000Z","uid":61520,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"236788b3cdafc0857d22a6c9036ab00a37feb1c9","tid":1589602,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:57:21.000Z","msg":"有唔少post 講popo 加黨鐵會令人唔敢到港島 於是提議各區， 小弟唔同意， 我地已經編地開花左成個月， 係時候要聚一聚全香港人既意志<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">既然港島唔俾我地去，我地就去將成個九龍尖咀旺角都企滿人<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"1bee3e0348ecd6d566fe11d4ad2fef4f74129896","tid":1589602,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:58:37.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n[一至五帶風向]教大家phone-in節目提高駁入直播室嘅成功率<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8991d2c6630ef67d646582543c6cbe3909271d51","tid":1589602,"uid":263680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:59:01.000Z","msg":"「整合」10月1日 分區/一區 優劣勢分析<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589523</a>"},{"pid":"1d17f96a1df6191f57916df081739b66541b9eef","tid":1589602,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:03:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"e289b0a91ce009353a94e3e29949f678592fa733","tid":1589602,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:10:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"355865e0226006ee6960fe70ee629cc1d3043c25","tid":1589602,"uid":124156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T11:10:45.000Z","msg":"「連登公投」10月1日 遍地開花 or 集中港島 ？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589615\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589615</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bf0808a74c8993d56b9663a2ee694af66aa09e4f","tid":1589602,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:26:35.000Z","msg":"【 9.28 + 10.1 】連發宣傳<br />\n<br />\n五年前的9月28日，催淚彈劃破夏愨道的半空，開展一場劍指真普選的佔領運動。<br />\n<br />\n五年過去，真普選雖仍遙遙無期，而警察比以前更黑、更暴力、更不受監管。但是，香港人履行了在當日佔領結束時許下的承諾 －「人民誓將歸來」。五年後的香港人，以更團結、更鏗鏘、更堅毅的姿態再次站到政權的面前，對抗警暴，爭取雙真普選。<br />\n<br />\n9月28日，作為一個我們都記得；我們都認為是重要的日子 － 雨傘運動五周年，我們希望和大家一同回到金鐘，在集會當中沉澱、思考。<br />\n<br />\n同時，縱然當前要舉辦一個合法的遊行是會被多番刁難，而部份手足亦已經視不反對通知書為廢紙，但我們仍入紙希望可以舉辦10.1遊行，盡力讓當日能夠有一個讓所有香港人都能夠參與的大遊行，因此約定大家，十月一日，維園見！<br />\n<br />\n【 9.28 反抗威權 迎接黎明 】集會<br />\n2019年9月28日<br />\n晚上7時至9時<br />\n金鐘添馬公園<br />\n<br />\n【 10.1 沒有國慶 只有國殤 】遊行<br />\n2019年10月1日<br />\n下午兩時起步<br />\n維園集合，遊行往遮打道<br />\n<br />\n主辦︰民間人權陣線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8Dkz2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8Dkz2M.jpg&h=c7d62bd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qS9jQCv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqS9jQCv.jpg&h=769335de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hqy41Ka.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHqy41Ka.jpg&h=a6dbaf1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WJQZQCw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWJQZQCw.jpg&h=ba39fbf6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YBnxrpS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYBnxrpS.jpg&h=5d06ca10&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}